Changelog for Hitman

x.x xxxx-xx-xx
 - Now using 2-columnm tabular format instead of QIIME for input mapping files
 - Input can now be SFF or FASTQ files
 - Argument --input is now used for all scripts to provide sequences
 - hitman_hire now has a --mapping argument separate from --input
 - Support for GZIP-compressed input files
 - Support for paired-end amplicon reads

0.1 2014-03-13
 - Initial version
